ygData.messageBody:
> So that's how I got my Yk!!!

Congrats. Well earned.

> p.s. LoD spanked Naggy - SOL-B is horrible with 70 plus in the zone.

Spanked? Try they had many casualities, and almost lost.

> p.s.s. ML and Storm got spanked by Voxxy and yielded the camp to LoD by
> prior agreement on a certain time. LoD prolly got Voxxy and Naggy in the
> same night.

What the f*ck? Were you there? Hell no you werent. You have no
clue as to what happened. We didn't get spanked at all. I'll share
with you what happened Ms. Naive.

LoD (ala FoH) does everything, they just dropped Nagafen, and threatened
to come take Vox next. The Vox teams rushed around trying to do it all
before LoD showed up and the was the first major problem. Then some
shaman pets got lose after pulling monk FD, and inadvertantly pulled
Vox right into the King Room. People paniced, and ran around, and then
chaos ensued. It really pisses me off that those mistakes were made,
but it even pisses me off more that you think we got spanked. We didn't
even fight Vox.

Irritated,
Harmonic.
